            "text": " We may now conclude by simple computations. For ease of notations, set  $a_2 = V_n(L_t, M, K[n-2])$ ,  $a_0 = V_n(K)$ ,  $a_t = V_n(L_t, L[n-1])$  and  $a_m = V_n(M, K[n-1])$ . We shall show that  $F_K(L_t, M) < 0$ , which rewrites as  $(a_t - a_0)a_m - (a_2 - a_m)a_0 < 0$ .",
